      "content": "Wait, you said Profile B might get a harsher sentence because of his background? That seems a bit counterintuitive if the judge is supposed to consider \"mitigating factors\" like systemic disadvantage. Shouldn't the lack of opportunity and unstable environment be seen as a reason to be more lenient or focus on rehabilitation rather than punishment?",
